336
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:46,050
Not everyone is like you, not having to leave home at a young age.

337
00:36:47,430 --> 00:36:52,330
Among these people whose homes are far away, how many left willingly?

338
00:36:59,700 --> 00:37:03,020
Young Lord, you are drinking too much.

339
00:37:03,020 --> 00:37:08,230
How to lessen grief? Only with Du Kang.
 (T/N: legendary inventor of wine)

