00:37:17,030 --> 00:37:19,520
This is one of them.

342
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:52,080
General Pei, look.

343
00:37:53,170 --> 00:37:58,720
Shangjing looks really pretty in the misty rain. It's like a drawing.

344
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:04,870
Even the best painter in Xi State probably couldn't imagine such a scene.

345
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:12,960
So much prosperity, such gentleness and humidity.

346
00:38:14,190 --> 00:38:17,500
