347
00:38:17,500 --> 00:38:20,930
It's like a fairy castle that gods favor the most.

348
00:38:22,710 --> 00:38:28,150
Tens of thousands of people come to greet and admire this capital of the Li Empire,

349
00:38:31,140 --> 00:38:33,800
