350
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:38,190
No matter how nice this place is, it is not my Xi State.

351
00:38:39,300 --> 00:38:44,080
General Pei, do you have a sweetheart?

352
00:38:48,300 --> 00:38:53,540
When you get married, you must marry someone you love.

353
00:38:54,170 --> 00:38:59,490
Otherwise, you'd be heartbroken and the other person would be, too.

354
00:39:02,890 --> 00:39:09,040
In a marriage without love, every day feels like a year's time.

355
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:15,460
It's like a dark night without end. I don't want you to also live such a life.

356
00:39:18,200 --> 00:39:23,980
I am a royal descendant. I have no control over my marriage.

357
00:39:25,250 --> 00:39:28,820
